svg:

name: swi
svg:
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="vector-effect: non-scaling-stroke;">
<g fill="blue" stroke="blue" id="swi" class="draggable-group" pointer-events="visible">
  <g id="xswi">
    <title>SWI</title>
	  <rect height="22" width="22" y="0" x="0" stroke="none" fill="none"/>
	  <circle class="XSWI" cx="10.5" cy="10.5" r="10" id="swi_status" onclick="open_control(evt,'swi_oper')">
      <animate id="open" attributeName="fill" to="none" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
      <animate id="close" attributeName="fill" to="inherit" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
	  </circle>
  
    <animate id="fail" attributeName="stroke" to="white" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
    <animate id="fail2" attributeName="fill" to="white" dur="100ms" begin="fail.begin" fill="freeze"/> 
    <animate id="normal" attributeName="stroke" to="inherit" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
    <animate id="normal2" attributeName="fill" to="inherit" dur="100ms" begin="normal.begin" fill="freeze"/> 
  </g>
</g>
</svg>

name: cbr
svg:
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="vector-effect: non-scaling-stroke;">
<g class="draggable-group" stroke="blue" fill="blue" id="cbr" pointer-events="visible">
  <g id="xcbr">
    <title>CBR</title>
    <rect height="22" width="22" y="0" x="0" stroke="none" fill="none"/>
    <rect height="20" width="20" y="1" x="1" class="XCBR" id="cbr_status" onclick="open_control(evt,'cbr_oper')">   
      <animate id="open" attributeName="fill" to="none" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/>
      <animate id="close" attributeName="fill" to="inherit" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
    </rect>

    <animate id="fail" attributeName="stroke" to="white" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
    <animate id="fail2" attributeName="fill" to="white" dur="100ms" begin="fail.begin" fill="freeze"/> 
    <animate id="normal" attributeName="stroke" to="inherit" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
    <animate id="normal2" attributeName="fill" to="inherit" dur="100ms" begin="normal.begin" fill="freeze"/> 
  </g>
</g>
</svg>

name: gnd

name: msr
svg:
<svg width="52" height="52" pointer-events="bounding-box" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
<!--
this is an interactive small DSO transformer station (dutch: MSR)

animations:

feed1: normal,fail
feed2: normal,fail
busbar: normal,fail
msr: normalall, failall (failall overrides normal of feeds, busbar, cbrs)

CBR1: error,open,transition,close - class:XCBR
CBR2: error,open,transition,close - class:XCBR
CBR3: error,open,transition,close - class:XCBR

earth1: close, open - class:XSWI
earth2: close, open - class:XSWI
earth3: close, open - class:XSWI

-->
 <g id="msr" fill="orange" stroke="orange" class="draggable-group" pointer-events="visible"><g>
  <title>MSR</title>
  <rect height="51" width="49" y="0" x="0" stroke="none" fill="none"/>

  <line id="feed1" y2="5.34582" x2="34.9091" y1="5.34582" x1="18" stroke="inherit" fill="none">
    <animate id="fail" attributeName="stroke" to="white" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
    <animate id="normal" attributeName="stroke" to="inherit" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
  </line>
  <g id="earth1_g">
    <ellipse class="XSWI" stroke-width="0.8" ry="3.39773" rx="3.39773" id="earth1_status" cy="5.49355" cx="38.64771" stroke="yellow" fill="none" onclick="open_control(evt,'earth1_oper')">
          <animate id="close" attributeName="fill" to="yellow" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
          <animate id="open" attributeName="fill" to="none" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
    </ellipse>
    <line id="svg_23" y2="5.18751" x2="45.50997" y1="5.18751" x1="42.37498" stroke="yellow" fill="none"/>
    <line id="svg_24" y2="8.20057" x2="45.99998" y1="2.81251" x1="45.99998" stroke="yellow" fill="none"/>
    <line id="svg_25" y2="7.18751" x2="47.37498" y1="3.68751" x1="47.37498" stroke="yellow" fill="none"/>
    <line id="svg_26" y2="6.49554" x2="48.87498" y1="4.31251" x1="48.87498" stroke="yellow" fill="none"/>
  </g>

  <g id="trafo">
    <line id="svg_5" y2="20.70946" x2="35.94666" y1="20.70946" x1="18" stroke="inherit" fill="none"/>
    <line id="svg_12" y2="20.6954" x2="25.87499" y1="33.11854" x1="25.87499" stroke="inherit" fill="none"/>
    <line id="svg_13" y2="33.539" x2="25.43957" y1="33.539" x1="35.07955" stroke="inherit" fill="none"/>
    <ellipse stroke-width="0.4" ry="3.39773" rx="3.39773" id="svg_20" cy="20.85718" cx="39.22726" stroke="inherit" fill="none"/>
    <ellipse stroke-width="0.4" ry="3.39773" rx="3.39773" id="svg_21" cy="20.85718" cx="42.22726" stroke="inherit" fill="none"/>

    <animate id="fail" attributeName="stroke" to="white" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
    <animate id="normal" attributeName="stroke" to="inherit" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
  </g>
  <g id="earth2_g">
    <ellipse class="XSWI" stroke-width="0.8" ry="3.39773" rx="3.39773" id="earth2_status" cy="33.26627" cx="38.64771" stroke="yellow" fill="none" onclick="open_control(evt,'earth2_oper')">
          <animate id="close" attributeName="fill" to="yellow" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
          <animate id="open" attributeName="fill" to="none" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
    </ellipse>
    <line id="svg_31" y2="33.3125" x2="45.50997" y1="33.3125" x1="42.37498" stroke="yellow" fill="none"/>
    <line id="svg_32" y2="36.32556" x2="45.99998" y1="30.9375" x1="45.99998" stroke="yellow" fill="none"/>
    <line id="svg_33" y2="35.3125" x2="47.37498" y1="31.8125" x1="47.37498" stroke="yellow" fill="none"/>
    <line id="svg_34" y2="34.62053" x2="48.87498" y1="32.4375" x1="48.87498" stroke="yellow" fill="none"/>
  </g>

  <line id="feed2" y2="46.70945" x2="35.30196" y1="46.70945" x1="18" stroke="inherit" fill="none">
    <animate id="fail" attributeName="stroke" to="white" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
    <animate id="normal" attributeName="stroke" to="inherit" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/>  
  </line>

  <g id="earth3_g">
    <ellipse class="XSWI" stroke-width="0.8" ry="3.39773" rx="3.39773" id="earth3_status" cy="46.56172" cx="38.89771" stroke="yellow" fill="none" onclick="open_control(evt,'earth3_oper')">
          <animate id="close" attributeName="fill" to="yellow" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
          <animate id="open" attributeName="fill" to="none" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
    </ellipse>
    <line id="svg_35" y2="46.4375" x2="45.50997" y1="46.4375" x1="42.37498" stroke="yellow" fill="none"/>
    <line id="svg_36" y2="49.45056" x2="45.99998" y1="44.0625" x1="45.99998" stroke="yellow" fill="none"/>
    <line id="svg_37" y2="48.4375" x2="47.37498" y1="44.9375" x1="47.37498" stroke="yellow" fill="none"/>
    <line id="svg_38" y2="47.74553" x2="48.87498" y1="45.5625" x1="48.87498" stroke="yellow" fill="none"/>
  </g>

  <g id="busbar">
    <line id="svg_3" y2="1.95172" x2="3.00001" y1="49.97081" x1="3.00001" stroke-width="1.6" stroke="inherit" fill="none"/>
    <line id="svg_5" y2="20.70946" x2="3" y1="20.70946" x1="13.49037" stroke="inherit" fill="none"/>
    <line id="svg_4" y2="5.34582" x2="13.49037" y1="5.34582" x1="3" stroke="inherit" fill="none"/>
    <line id="svg_14" y2="46.70945" x2="13.49037" y1="46.70945" x1="3" stroke="inherit" fill="none"/>

    <rect id="cbr1_status" class="XCBR" height="4.43182" width="4.43182" y="2.98219" x="13.49037" stroke="inherit" fill="inherit" onclick="open_control(evt,'cbr1_oper')">
        <animate id="open" attributeName="fill" to="none" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/>
        <animate id="close" attributeName="fill" to="inherit" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
    </rect>
    <rect id="cbr2_status" class="XCBR" height="4.43182" width="4.43182" y="18.34582" x="13.49037" stroke="inherit" fill="inherit" onclick="open_control(evt,'cbr2_oper')">
        <animate id="open" attributeName="fill" to="none" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/>
        <animate id="close" attributeName="fill" to="inherit" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
    </rect>
    <rect id="cbr3_status" class="XCBR" height="4.43182" width="4.43182" y="44.51627" x="13.49037" stroke="inherit" fill="inherit" onclick="open_control(evt,'cbr3_oper')">
        <animate id="open" attributeName="fill" to="none" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/>
        <animate id="close" attributeName="fill" to="inherit" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
    </rect>
    <animate id="fail" attributeName="stroke" to="white" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
    <animate id="fail2" attributeName="fill" to="white" dur="100ms" fill="freeze" begin="fail.begin"/> 
    <animate id="normal" attributeName="stroke" to="inherit" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
    <animate id="normal2" attributeName="fill" to="inherit" dur="100ms" fill="freeze" begin="normal.begin"/> 
  </g>

  <animate id="failall" attributeName="stroke" to="white" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
  <animate id="failall2" attributeName="fill" to="white" dur="100ms" begin="failall.begin" fill="freeze"/> 
  <animate id="normalall" attributeName="stroke" to="inherit" dur="100ms" fill="freeze"/> 
  <animate id="normalall2" attributeName="fill" to="inherit" dur="100ms" begin="normalall.begin" fill="freeze"/> 
 </g>
</g>
</svg>

name: vt
svg:
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="vector-effect: non-scaling-stroke;">
  <g id="vt" fill="white" stroke="none">
    <title>VTR</title>
    <text id="voltage_value" class="MEAS" data-text="Voltage: {value} V" fill="inherit" stroke="inherit" x="0" y="10" font-size="12" font-family="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" text-anchor="start" xml:space="preserve" font-weight="normal" font-style="normal" onclick="open_control(evt,'voltage_value')">--- Voltage: {value} V ---</text>
  </g>
</svg>

name: ct
svg:
<svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" style="vector-effect: non-scaling-stroke;">
  <g id="ct" fill="white" stroke="none">
    <title>CTR</title>
    <text id="current_value" class="MEAS" data-text="Current: {value} A" fill="inherit" stroke="inherit" x="0" y="10" font-size="12" font-family="Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif" text-anchor="start" xml:space="preserve" font-weight="normal" font-style="normal" onclick="open_control(evt,'current_value')">--- Current: {value} A ---</text>
  </g>
</svg>
